Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,全員戒備!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.57,0:23:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,全員…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.12,0:23:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,給我狠狠地打!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.09,0:23:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,冰結術!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.67,0:24:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人跟上那兩個蠢貨!
